column6: Anup Baral,4.1M,18.6K,0,948,1.6M,ne,"Jeevan Jung Thapa (Saugat Malla) is a loyal and hard-working police inspector. Desperate to solve the case in order to gain promotion and live a happy life, he is left with nothing but his house which is marked for demolition, a worried wife and kid, and all the anger needed to solve the cliff-hanging case.
